DELHI NCR SECURITY SERVICES
Company Profile
Overview
Delhi NCR Security Services is a guarding service and Electronic Security Systems Company of India. We provide a single
window service for any security requirement. It has always been our endeavor to offer total security solutions
customized to the clients’ need at realistic & affordable prices.
Clientele
Today Delhi NCR Security Services is the most professional & quality conscious versatile Security & Detective agency in
the national capital region. It is capable of providing total security requirements to Government, Semi government
Undertaking Banks, Industrial Houses, Multinational companies, and Private Organizations like Hospitals, Factories,
Academic institutions, Residences etc.
Services
Delhi NCR Security Services undertakes security assignments including Uniformed Guarding Services, Integrated Access
Control and Security Systems, Gate & Door Automation Systems, Intruder Fire Alarm Systems, Closed Circuit
Surveillances Systems, Wireless Communication Systems.
Professional Team
The company is incorporated under the company’s act 1956 with its Head Office at New Delhi. Apart from the
company’s permanent staff it has the series of experts in business & commercial security, industrial security, private
investigations, personnel management & finance as advisors & consultants on retainership basis.
With Delhi NCR Security Services, clients are assured of a long term Security partner who shall stand by you in your of
need.
Verticals

 Security Management
 Guest House Management Services
 Facility Management Services

Service Highlights
ASSIGNMENT MANAGER
We assign a full time qualified Manager with proven experience in the field to the contract, with a full support team.
QUALITY AUDIT TEAM
The Team is responsible for the monitoring the performance & ensures that the land down quality standard are adhered
Whatever believes that the best result for any assignment is possible if we deploy our quality audit team to such a
period that allows us to co-ordinate and streamline the security systems and also introduce new inceptors and systems
where applicable after mutual agreement.
EXTERNAL SUPERVISION
Mobile Sector Field officers check every site on a daily basis both at night as well as in the day.
EMERGENCIES
Our office is manned on a round the clock basis. There is a Security Officer on duty in the control Room and he is
supported by a mobile patrol. They are desired to handle every type of emergency at night and on holidays.
MANAGEMENT MEETINGS
Our operation Manager visits the site once in a fortnight to discuss mutual problem. Additionally, he is available for
meeting of emergencies whenever there is a requirement.

Housekeeping Services
We believe that clean environment accentuates overall productivity and workplace-
efficiency for any productive facility. A properly-maintained premise promotes
employee welfare and satisfaction, giving an undeniable stimulus to efficiency
and employee productivity. Therefore, every establishment or office needs
cleaning and housekeeping services. To promote an environment that is
clean and clear and spotless, we at Delhi NCR recruit the best office
cleaners and janitorial cleaning services
At Delhi NCR Security Services, we are equipped in providing par amount
housekeeping services and cleaning services to our clients. Whether it’s a
cleaning for health drive, cleaning for a reason or just festival cleaning (like
cleaning for Christmas, Diwali), Delhi NCR Security Services cleaning solutions
always guarantee best results.
To offer pioneering cleaning services, we deploy cleaners with field expertise, ensuring all statutory cleaning
staff guidelines are strictly adhered to. After recruitment, we impart a decisive program aimed at cleaning staff
training, showing the best and fastest ways of cleaning toilets, cleaning windows, cleaning office premises and cleaning of
bathroom tiles. As cleanliness in any premise is enforced through diligent care of cleanliness and surroundings, our
office and industrial cleaning services are well versed with commercial cleaning practices. These often include contract
cleaning services for floor cleaning, glass cleaning, on-site dry carpet cleaning and housekeeping services.

RATE STRUCTURE
The rates are based on the minimum wages and are the prevailing rates in scheduled employments, covered under the
Minimum Wages Act.
Terms & Conditions:
1) The above costing includes: Uniform, Relievers, Supervision, and Minimum wage with Statutory obligations.
2) Charges for any additional duty performed beyond the contractual rates, shall be on pro rata basis as per
negotiation.
3) Detailed terms and conditions would be mentioned in the agreement which would be required prior to
deployment of guards.
We shall provide you quality and standard guards with the following standards of recruitment system:-
a. Height: 5 ft. 8 in. and above.
b. Eye Sight : 6 X 6
c. Physique : Healthy
d. Education: Matriculate duties Experience preferred.
e. Experience: Industry security duties Experience preferred.
f. Age: 25 to 40 Years.
Duties and responsibility of security guard:-
1) Entries of inward and outward register of material, machine etc
2) Entries of following register:-
(a) Daily Muster Roll
(b) Daily occurrence Book
(c) Daily Report Book
(d) Duty Individual Card
(e) Attendance Sheet
(f) Visitor's Register
(g) Vehicle movement register
(h) Out/ In register etc.
3) Frisking and checking of lower staff.
4) Handle any special circumstances or incidence.
5) Regular inspections of fire safety equipment & First response to fire and other emergencies
